"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1927539-andy-murray-Olympics-2024-plan\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murraywill not compete in the singles event at theOlympic Games, instead focusing his attention on the doubles competition with fellow Brit Dan Evans.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray was entered into both the singles and doubles events, but the three-time Grand Slam champion will only take part in the doubles in what will be his last ever tennis tournament.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On his participation in Paris, Murray said on Wednesday night: \\\"I need to make that decision this evening.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997867924094, \"rank\": 2.1320759033185373e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not think so.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, me and Dan have made the commitment to each other that that was what we would prioritise.\\\"\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And on Thursday morning, the news of his withdrawal was confirmed.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I have take the decision to withdraw from the singles to concentrate on the doubles with Dan.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our practice has been great and we are playing well together.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Really looking forward to getting started and representing GB one more time.\\\"\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9958712883450053, \"rank\": 0.004145191044276113, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On his decision to call it a day from tennis, Murray revealed he's both 'physically and mentally' ready to stop.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-timeWimbledonwinner toldSky Sports: \\\"Physically I think my body is ready to stop, mentally I am ready to finish playing.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is also an event that is really special to me, I have loved being part of this team for the last four or five Olympic Games and I am happy that I get to finish playing here.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd had the conversation about when I would finish with my family and team, I'd spoken about it last year and spoke about it this year.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was still unsure about it [the exact time].\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like I was going to finish this summer, whether that be after Wimbledon or after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"It just felt like it was going to be the right time, I got the injury to my ankle in March and then obviously got the back injury at Queen's and had to have the operation.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although I was unsure a few months ago about when to stop, I knew when I had the surgery on my back it was the right time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray already boasts two Olympic gold medals to his name, having triumphed at Wimbledon in 2016, before defending his crown at the Rio Games four years later.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on his connection with the Games, Murray said: \\\"Every time I have come to the Olympics it feels totally different [to other tennis events] and I personally love it.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it has been an amazing experience.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love being around athletes, being part of the team, representing my country.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it has been right up there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray announced on Tuesday that the Olympics in Paris would be his final tournament as a tennis player, bringing an end to his formidable 19-year professional career.\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2562, \"end\": 2568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997867924094, \"rank\": 2.1320759033185373e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Posting an emotional statement on X, Murray said: \\\"Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament @Olympics Competing for (Team GB).\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2768, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997867924094, \"rank\": 2.1320759033185373e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I am extremely proud to get to do it one final time!\\\"\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  It came as no surprise, given the tennis ace had little intention to carry on competing beyond the summer.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there had been some suggestions Murray might've fancied bowing out at the US Open, given it was the first Grand Slam he won 12 years ago.\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3376, \"end\": 3382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.055853760594509e-18, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3620